lexicalizations.pl lexicalizations stimuli

# line breaks need to be inserted by hand; criteria:
# the following must not be separated by a line breat:
#
#   1 word + direct object + critical region (verb) + 2 words
#   (spillover) + 1 word 
#
# for the subordinate claus (first critical region) the spillover can
# be reduced to one word
#
# the extra word at the beginning and end should be at leat 4
# characters
#
# the second critical region always has to be on the same line (this
# is not possible for the first critical region)
